<bibRefCitation author="Ahrens, D. &amp; Fabrizi, S." box="[921,1187,223,250]" pageId="157" pageNumber="158" pagination="1 - 355" refId="ref330518" refString="Ahrens, D. &amp; Fabrizi, S. (2016) A Monograph of the Sericini of India (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae). Bonn Zoological Bulletin, 65, 1 - 355." type="journal article" year="2016">Ahrens &amp; Fabrizi 2016</bibRefCitation>
